WEBVTT


00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:32.560
Lu Chengwen.

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:34.560
What are you doing here again?

00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:36.120
I asked him to come.

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:39.840
Mr. Tie,

00:01:39.959 --> 00:01:41.959
we've pretty much discussed all the details.

00:01:42.319 --> 00:01:43.719
How about we head back to the company

00:01:43.719 --> 00:01:45.120
to transfer the funds and sign the contract?

00:01:45.319 --> 00:01:46.120
Mr. Lu,

00:01:46.319 --> 00:01:47.840
should we discuss this later?

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:49.959
This fund

00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:52.000
is for our Qianfeng Group

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.560
to invest in the amusement park.

00:01:54.359 --> 00:01:55.519
It has nothing to do with him.

00:01:57.799 --> 00:01:58.359
Mr. Lu,

00:01:58.359 --> 00:01:58.840
is...

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:00.120
is that so?

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:03.319
Is that so?

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:11.719
The CEO of Qianfeng Group is right here.

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.319
Let's just

00:02:13.319 --> 00:02:14.199
be frank.

00:02:14.520 --> 00:02:16.000
It is indeed for Qianfeng.

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:17.319
But,

00:02:17.319 --> 00:02:18.439
I think

00:02:18.759 --> 00:02:20.759
the construction project in the old south city

00:02:20.759 --> 00:02:21.599
has more potential.

00:02:21.960 --> 00:02:22.960
Right, right, right, right.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:23.960
Then this money will...

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:24.759
Mr. Tie,

00:02:25.039 --> 00:02:26.000
don't forget,

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:27.439
you came here this time

00:02:27.439 --> 00:02:28.800
because you were entrusted by someone

00:02:29.039 --> 00:02:31.000
to invest in our amusement park.

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:32.360
Oh?

00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:34.360
Entrusted by someone?

00:02:35.159 --> 00:02:36.400
Entrusted by whom?

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:38.159
Yeah.

00:02:38.439 --> 00:02:39.800
I'm here to help the Young Master...

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.319
Okay.

00:02:41.319 --> 00:02:43.360
I'm just here to invest in good projects.

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:45.520
I trust Mr. Lu's judgment.

00:02:45.639 --> 00:02:46.719
Whatever Mr. Lu invests in,

00:02:46.719 --> 00:02:47.599
I'll invest in.

00:02:48.759 --> 00:02:49.000
Wait,

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.039
you're just a vice president,

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:51.439
why do you talk so much nonsense?

00:02:56.039 --> 00:02:57.840
Did you mistake him for someone else?

00:02:58.319 --> 00:02:59.120
Mistake who?

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.759
Your CEO is in my Young Master's arms.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:02.840
This idiot.

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.120
He exposed me.

00:03:05.639 --> 00:03:08.120
Please open your eyes wide and look,

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:09.960
I am your Young Master.

00:03:13.000 --> 00:03:13.800
Darn it.

00:03:13.919 --> 00:03:15.120
It's completely over.

00:03:17.439 --> 00:03:19.919
You're pretending to be my Young Master?

00:03:20.199 --> 00:03:21.919
Don't you know what you look like?

00:03:21.919 --> 00:03:22.400
You...

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:23.360
You what?

00:03:23.599 --> 00:03:25.400
Do you know what a Young Master is?

00:03:25.759 --> 00:03:26.639
Suave and elegant,

00:03:26.639 --> 00:03:27.560
dignified and imposing,

00:03:27.759 --> 00:03:28.599
surrounded by beauties,

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:30.039
enjoying the company of multiple women.

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:31.759
That's a fucking Young Master.

00:03:31.759 --> 00:03:32.719
Now look at you.

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.120
Looking like a loser,

00:03:34.120 --> 00:03:35.120
tough on the outside, weak on the inside,

00:03:35.520 --> 00:03:36.639
just an ant.

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:38.360
Still pretending to be a God of War?

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:39.159
I...

00:03:39.759 --> 00:03:40.560
Enough.

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:41.759
Old Tie,

00:03:41.759 --> 00:03:42.960
you, you, you...

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:43.960
What's wrong with you?

00:03:44.199 --> 00:03:45.599
Why are you always causing trouble?

00:03:46.199 --> 00:03:47.000
How about this?

00:03:47.159 --> 00:03:48.000
Tomorrow, um...

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.240
you go to Qianfeng Group

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:50.560
and talk to Ms. Leng.

00:03:51.039 --> 00:03:51.960
You can go back first.

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:52.560
Okay.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.319
Understood.

00:03:58.560 --> 00:03:59.159
Brother Zhantian,

00:03:59.159 --> 00:04:00.000
are you okay?

00:04:00.520 --> 00:04:01.199
You get

00:04:01.199 --> 00:04:01.759
lost!

00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:03.759
Okay, okay, okay.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:04.800
Then I'll

00:04:04.800 --> 00:04:06.159
take her and leave first.

00:04:06.639 --> 00:04:07.439
Let's go.

00:04:10.639 --> 00:04:11.439
Lu Chengwen.

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:13.199
You ruined my plan again.

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:18.839
Brother Chengwen,

00:04:18.959 --> 00:04:20.560
if helping people makes you unhappy,

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.959
you shouldn't have agreed.

00:04:22.759 --> 00:04:23.800
By the way, Brother Chengwen,

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:25.000
what exactly are you worried about?

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.160
Gu Zhantian.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.639
His target isn't just the Leng family,

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:30.199
but the four major families of Haicheng.

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:31.439
What?

00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:33.399
Let's join forces.

00:04:33.399 --> 00:04:34.399
We'll deal with him together.

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:36.639
No.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:39.040
You guys have no idea how powerful he is.

00:04:39.639 --> 00:04:40.720
Brother Chengwen,

00:04:40.959 --> 00:04:42.560
a mighty dragon can't crush a local snake.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:44.360
Haicheng is our home turf.

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:46.199
Why are you being so negative?

00:04:46.399 --> 00:04:47.120
Brother Chengwen,

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:48.000
don't forget,

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.800
you're the number one bad boy in Haicheng.

00:04:50.639 --> 00:04:53.639
This isn't about dragons or being bad.

00:04:54.600 --> 00:04:55.000
Forget it.

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.360
I can't explain it to you clearly.

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:58.199
You guys,

00:04:58.199 --> 00:04:59.399
stop pestering me.

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:00.360
Zhao Gang,

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.600
drop me off by the road.

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:02.759
Take them home.

00:05:08.360 --> 00:05:09.160
Sure enough,

00:05:09.519 --> 00:05:11.560
there's only one unchanging law in life,

00:05:11.959 --> 00:05:13.519
and that is you reap what you sow.

00:05:13.959 --> 00:05:15.560
If I hadn't messed around,

00:05:15.959 --> 00:05:17.439
the plot wouldn't have collapsed like this.

00:05:17.759 --> 00:05:19.560
Can I still survive until Gu Zhantian

00:05:19.639 --> 00:05:21.319
unites Haicheng in the finale?

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:23.519
Defier of Fate.

00:05:24.439 --> 00:05:26.120
According to the time flow of the novel world,

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:27.639
in the real world,

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:29.519
how much time is left

00:05:29.519 --> 00:05:30.360
until my mom's surgery?

00:05:30.759 --> 00:05:33.240
Nine hours, 32 minutes, and 45 seconds.

00:05:33.600 --> 00:05:34.399
Lu Chengwen,

00:05:34.759 --> 00:05:36.120
in the novel world,

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:37.759
you have less than four days left.

00:05:38.319 --> 00:05:39.319
You should understand

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.199
what your current plot and direction

00:05:41.199 --> 00:05:42.319
represent.

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:43.959
I understand.

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:46.800
Time

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:47.600
is running out.

00:05:48.399 --> 00:05:49.199
Lu Chengwen,

00:05:49.439 --> 00:05:50.959
what's meant to come will come.

00:06:31.959 --> 00:06:32.720
Brother Zhantian,

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:34.319
I was wrong.

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:35.959
I beg you, don't kill me.

00:06:35.959 --> 00:06:37.160
I'll do whatever you ask.

00:06:37.319 --> 00:06:38.120
Shut up.

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:39.720
Before I get the funds,

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:40.720
you won't die.

00:06:41.720 --> 00:06:42.759
What are you going to do?

00:06:43.040 --> 00:06:44.040
Don't disturb the young master.

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:45.160
He's preparing to channel his energy.

00:06:45.199 --> 00:06:46.399
The Face-Swapping Technique.

00:06:47.000 --> 00:06:47.959
Face-Swapping Technique?

00:06:48.439 --> 00:06:49.800
It means swapping your faces

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:50.959
for a certain period

00:06:50.959 --> 00:06:51.839
of time.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:52.839
However, young master,

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:54.360
this will cause your combat power

00:06:54.360 --> 00:06:55.959
to drop significantly for a few days.

00:06:56.439 --> 00:06:57.720
Here,

00:06:57.720 --> 00:06:59.120
we don't need fighting and killing.

00:06:59.720 --> 00:07:01.439
What we need

00:07:01.439 --> 00:07:02.800
is to use our brains.

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:51.000
How do they have all these weird moves?

00:07:51.399 --> 00:07:52.839
As a villain, besides having money,

00:07:52.839 --> 00:07:53.600
I'm absolutely nothing.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:54.560
How am I supposed to play this?

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:55.720
Young master,

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:57.920
this face-swapping consumed too much of your power.

00:07:57.959 --> 00:07:58.920
Can you still handle it?

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:00.160
It's fine.

00:08:00.759 --> 00:08:02.000
The top priority right now

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:03.560
is to quickly get back those five billion.

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:05.199
I'll be right back.

00:08:05.319 --> 00:08:06.399
You keep watch here.

00:08:17.759 --> 00:08:19.120
When Gu Zhantian comes back,

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:20.399
I'm dead meat.

00:08:20.759 --> 00:08:21.560
No.

00:08:21.639 --> 00:08:22.720
I need to figure something out.

00:08:23.839 --> 00:08:24.639
Right.

00:08:24.920 --> 00:08:25.720
The Flash Card.

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:27.560
You're not the only ones with magic items.

00:08:27.639 --> 00:08:28.720
I have them too.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:41.799
Darn it.

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:43.480
I flashed to the wrong place.

00:08:44.559 --> 00:08:45.360
Gu Zhantian!

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:46.320
What are you doing?

00:08:50.559 --> 00:08:51.720
I'm Lu Chengwen!

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:53.120
I can prove it!

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:55.159
Help!

00:08:57.320 --> 00:08:58.320
Help!

00:08:58.320 --> 00:08:58.960
Calm down, calm down.

00:08:58.960 --> 00:09:00.159
Listen to what I'm thinking.

00:09:00.159 --> 00:09:00.759
Calm down.

00:09:00.759 --> 00:09:01.559
Mengyun.

00:09:02.159 --> 00:09:04.200
You're with the person you like,

00:09:04.559 --> 00:09:05.320
and then

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:06.960
you get married and have kids.

00:09:07.159 --> 00:09:08.399
Then a family of three...

00:09:08.799 --> 00:09:09.519
That

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:10.200
would be so happy.

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:11.039
Right?

00:09:14.039 --> 00:09:14.840
Chengwen,

00:09:17.559 --> 00:09:18.960
why do you look like this?

00:09:23.639 --> 00:09:24.919
My face was swapped.

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:26.639
I can't explain it right now.

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:28.320
Hurry and take me to Qianfeng Group.

00:09:28.559 --> 00:09:29.840
You're going to find Leng Qingqiu?

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:31.480
Qingqiu still doesn't know

00:09:31.480 --> 00:09:32.919
Gu Zhantian swapped faces with me.

00:09:33.039 --> 00:09:34.000
It's very dangerous.

00:09:40.159 --> 00:09:40.960
Mengyun,

00:09:41.799 --> 00:09:42.799
please, please.

00:09:44.759 --> 00:09:46.120
Whatever you want to do,

00:09:46.399 --> 00:09:48.000
haven't I always supported you?

00:09:49.720 --> 00:09:51.279
But,

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:52.200
I have a condition.

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:01.799
This has always been my wish.

00:10:02.039 --> 00:10:03.000
Do you agree?

00:10:05.960 --> 00:10:07.000
Okay.

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.480
How about we first

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:09.759
deal with this matter?

00:10:10.919 --> 00:10:11.720
Okay?